item.title: Why do i get this error?
item.dc:creator: @PaulT PaulT
item.description:
@PaulT wrote:

If you have started a new server and you are still getting the “Error connecting” over and over (which I think is what he means javac?) , there are a few things you can try to fix this. Try downloading the cache manually, updating your java, and exiting all other programs before playing.

Good luck!
